Purpose
=======
'smake' is a collection of qmake and GNU make scripts that automate the
creation of libraries and applications.

Implementation Notes
====================
The following URL is a good example where undocumented qmake functionality is
used extensively, such as export and the use of tests as procedures.

https://qt.gitorious.org/qt/qtbase/blobs/e3554d72745d9c439b1792c20be09871506afeef/mkspecs/features/qt_functions.prf
